  "description": "苹果2013年全球开发者大会（WWDC）在美国旧金山Moscone Center West举行。<b> 在本次大会上，苹果正式推出了iOS 7和OS X Mavericks。但由于苹果WWDC主要是面向开发者的会议，硬件方面并不是重点，只发布了一款全新的苹果Mac Pro台式机，更新了MacBook Air以及推出了新一代AirPort和新的时间胶囊。</b><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d1b5fee/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240673.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%96%B0Mac+Pro%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81+%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E7%89%88Air%E6%9C%AA%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240673.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%96%B0Mac+Pro%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81+%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E7%89%88Air%E6%9C%AA%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240673.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%96%B0Mac+Pro%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81+%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E7%89%88Air%E6%9C%AA%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240673.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%96%B0Mac+Pro%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81+%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E7%89%88Air%E6%9C%AA%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240673.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B