  "description": "<b>在今天凌晨的苹果2013年全球开发者大会（WWDC）上，处理器全面更新的MacBook&#160;Air正式亮相。在发布会之后，我们看到苹果中国官网及苹果香港官网也对其进行了更新。</b>我们在苹果中国官网中看到，包括今天发布的两款不同版本的11英寸和13英寸机型均已经更新，其中，配备128GB的11英寸版本机型售价7388元；256GB版本机型售价8888元；而两款13英寸的机型售价分别为7988元和9688元。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d1b5fec/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240672.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%B0Air%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89+%E8%B5%B7%E4%BB%B77388%E5%85%83%E6%AF%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B4%B5%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240672.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%B0Air%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89+%E8%B5%B7%E4%BB%B77388%E5%85%83%E6%AF%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B4%B5%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240672.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%B0Air%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89+%E8%B5%B7%E4%BB%B77388%E5%85%83%E6%AF%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B4%B5%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240672.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%B0Air%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89+%E8%B5%B7%E4%BB%B77388%E5%85%83%E6%AF%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B4%B5%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://